  "description": "# Surface Soil Moisture Product\nA experimental dataset of soil-moisture retrievals at 1km effective spatial resolution for all 28 basins of the Mediterranean study-area. The data was processed via the RT1 radiative transfer model using Sentinel-1 (VV) backscatter data together with auxiliary CGLS Leaf Area Index timeseries.\n",
